{"tid":1413771,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【有支国旗丟落海】香港眾星微博齊齊發聲：我是護旗手！","createTime":"2019-08-05T10:53:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T08:10:25.000Z","uid":184679,"like":16,"dislike":505,"uniUserReply":119,"replies":[{"pid":"d18e1e9236e13389edf2853d04614f34fa853797","tid":1413771,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T10:53:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2415000/2419434/china_thumb_20190805_S_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2415000%2F2419434%2Fchina_thumb_20190805_S_600.jpg&h=06e76278&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港反修例行動持續，8月3日的旺角遊行中有示威者於尖沙咀天星碼頭拆下旗桿上的國旗丟入海中，引起內地官方強烈反彈。<br />\n<br />\n內地官媒中央電視台連日來在微博上貼出一張五星國旗圖片，寫上「#五星紅旗有14億護旗手#」呼籲轉載，行動獲得成龍、Angelababy（楊穎）等香港藝人轉發響應，高呼「我是護旗手！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2415000/2419434/002_600.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2415000%2F2419434%2F002_600.JPG&h=b302673a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n自示威者丟國旗入海事件發生後，央視昨日（4日）起便陸續發布數條微博，發起「#五星紅旗有14億護旗手＃」的話題行動，號召網民轉發國旗圖片。<br />\n<br />\n央視今日（5日）上午亦發布微博指，相關行動「燃爆全網」，並批評「此前在港辱我國旗的一小撮末路渣徒，終將逃不脫法網。他們在億萬護旗手的眼中，不過是幾隻臭蟲」。截至今日（5日）下午，行動已在微博上創造逾22億的閲讀量，成為微博上的網絡熱話。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2415000/2419434/003_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2415000%2F2419434%2F003_600.jpg&h=4ef8ae59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相關行動除在內地網民獲得廣大迴響外，不少香港藝人包括成龍、Angelababy（楊穎）、劉愷威、陳小春也在微博上響應號召，轉載相關微博帖文，表示自己是護旗手。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2419434</code></pre>"},{"pid":"86cf07630106ddfcaa421186f96cd7a040ecbd42","tid":1413771,"uid":4574,"like":174,"dislike":1,"score":173,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T10:54:27.000Z","msg":"玻璃心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b1bd905a03077a574e7fff26a5bd8a4201d329e","tid":1413771,"uid":88982,"like":483,"dislike":1,"score":482,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T10:55:44.000Z","msg":"香港眾<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">暗</span></span>星"},{"pid":"231ca493d70988efe7c87b923708341e52534d16","tid":1413771,"uid":22063,"like":258,"dislike":1,"score":257,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T10:56:32.000Z","msg":"做對了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n揼多百零支落海，解放軍出關不是夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69b4b1e193d83a8e9bfa6baa659ab48cc13e01b2","tid":1413771,"uid":109923,"like":176,"dislike":3,"score":173,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T10:56:55.000Z","msg":"有支國旗跌落水 跌掉海 跌掉水"},{"pid":"4db8d5d84590f864e0848462204f0f838409e706","tid":1413771,"uid":59700,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T10:57:22.000Z","msg":"咁下次跳出黎護旗"},{"pid":"3e8c6bb63960ea0f6bfe4afcf32e45020febd550","tid":1413771,"uid":61439,"like":148,"dislike":2,"score":146,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T10:58:01.000Z","msg":"護旗不力係咪要問責先？"},{"pid":"638305ed2ba724eecf376d14e6e5026675ff84b2","tid":1413771,"uid":55951,"like":69,"dislike":1,"score":68,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T10:58:01.000Z","msg":"鍵盤愛國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n落現場護旗囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02e937baa374857859ba327ffce4abdb21fd60e9","tid":1413771,"uid":66221,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T10:58:04.000Z","msg":"中間果個邊個黎架，再嘈掟埋佢落海呀"},{"pid":"2c55f15f88a4cc91da0c34320a43aa53027ab4bc","tid":1413771,"uid":34010,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T10:58:07.000Z","msg":"咪又係飛落海 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3941618ff76382baae8bbaf714928f455d5a9d8","t